Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--text--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙躲到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖伊乌斯大人  从海流上考虑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是朝岛的西南方向去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您看如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去隆狄尼姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆狄尼姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.36,0:00:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  大战前要那个啥来着的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧  也这样通知士兵们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让城堡复活  我们已经解除了「生命之门」的坚固结界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他们发现是早晚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开战的话  一切都还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽这么说  但他们不会等我们摆好阵势
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器也还不够充足
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要统整好我们的军势呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去玩了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南瓜瓜瓜  南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么多  晚饭应该够吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆莉斯小姐  艾露敏小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚饭做盖尔火锅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…盖尔火锅真是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火锅吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  是火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈祷不是螃蟹火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在这儿偷懒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷懒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易回到我阔别已久的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我怀念一下故乡不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让人民挨饿  族长带头打猎  这是盖尔族的规定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  那个我已经听厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那么多  给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别扯啊  喂  快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  全部抓起来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太安静了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有其他人在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  这里是其他部族的狩猎区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能擅自闯入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找别的狩猎区吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩真是的  喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况怎么能不喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有肉的盖尔火锅…根本算不上盖尔火锅！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有活力真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…谁是猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:31.83,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：猴子的日文发音就是撒鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿尔撒鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你这第一战士工作不积极
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才落到连肉都吃不上的这步田地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩别这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别老「摩」「摩」地叫我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是牛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子  我第二战士摩尔嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为第一战士的宝座  向你提出决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人  不做点什么的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位  这是族长命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场决斗我允许了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要这种时候才摆出族长的架子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑  猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿起剑来和我决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  阿隆  快想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要有点第一战士的气概  自己解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥伽姆大人快想想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  老是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦  摩尔嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一口气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥伽姆  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是竖琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…这真是稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔撒鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呀  不认识的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在举行宴会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热爱歌唱和音乐的流浪的吟游诗人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是塔列辛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  吟游诗人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是稀奇  居然能在这附近遇上吟游诗人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听一听我这来自大陆的歌声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让宴会气氛热烈起来  再合适不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算礼貌一点说  今天的收获也不算丰盛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有果物的火锅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  让我用歌声为你们打气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心  代价只要把你们采来的蘑菇分一点给我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不错的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  受您夸奖真是光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  你们难道说是…盖尔族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是帝国那边的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是打算把我们的事告诉帝国吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个不错的想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀不好  待太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  告诉你们一件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近是被称为布利冈第斯族的山贼的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来已经明白了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就在此告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔列辛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你给大家带来了快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定还有机会唱给你们听的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  盖伊乌斯他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:12:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  似乎是追着那些蛮族来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  只要他们行动起来  钱就会滚滚而来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我赚上一笔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆狄尼姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论什么时候来都是个老旧的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆狄尼姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  从这里向南
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿鲁比昂岛最大的贸易都市  属于神圣帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  一口气攻进敌人的据点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近狩猎一点都不够爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里痒痒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  别急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  害怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  魔王怎么会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是  总之先去观光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  这城市真大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是隆狄尼姆  真是热闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是酒场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种各样的人聚在这里  好像很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瓦隆城里只有盖尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么突然干什么啊  阿尔撒鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在闹市中大喊大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的身份暴露了该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份精力就留到正式战斗再释放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是精力旺盛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么观光也到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  来自神圣帝国本土的物资全都经过这个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运送到各个前线基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  按照计划行事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖伊乌斯大人  差不多该去把那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  别心急
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖伊乌斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大一个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我们不去迎接  对方也会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…故意来我们的地盘这样的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不会做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的对手可是魔王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个「不可能」对我们来说正是好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫阿尔撒鲁  乖乖丢下行李离开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个蛮族能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩尔嘉  借你的弓箭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国的手下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖伊乌斯的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也是沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可没时间丧气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快会接到通报  赶过来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能反击了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔撒鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方的数量都没弄清楚就打算反击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们被耍了  怎么能就这样回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算带着那份懊悔和愤怒战斗  也无法获得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪  阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆  去狩猎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是螃蟹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么快就出现了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和螃蟹不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥伽姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是…


